      "description": "Hey there! You have seriously gotta see this beauty\u2014it\u2019s in absolutely incredible shape, honestly like it just rolled off the showroom floor. I\u2019ve pampered this car since day one, and it still has that fresh feel and drives like a total dream. No scratches, no dents, and the interior is just spotless! If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s been loved and looks brand new, this is the one. Drop me a message and come take it for a spin!",
