    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a superlative example of the marque, meticulously maintained to an exacting mechanical standard. The S54 3.2L inline-six delivers a linear power band through its six individual throttle bodies, with the high-pressure double VANOS system recently overhauled using Beisan components for total reliability. The chassis has undergone a comprehensive subframe reinforcement, paired with a precision-tuned suspension featuring Bilstein PSS10 dampers and refreshed polyurethane bushings. Power is transferred via a Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox to a variable M-differential lock, ensuring optimal traction and corner-exit stability. Every factory panel retains its original finish with no evidence of oxidation, and the undercarriage is free of typical corrosion. This is a turn-key, collector-grade machine prepared for the discerning driver who prioritizes mechanical integrity and performance-focused provenance.",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 15
    },
    {
