    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly museum-grade vehicle that looks and drives as if it just left the showroom floor. This car has been strictly garage-kept in a climate-controlled environment, preserving the deep, mirror-like luster of its original factory paint\u2014completely free of stone chips, swirl marks, or door dings. The interior is a time capsule; the premium leather remains supple with no bolster wear, the carpets are spotless, and it retains that distinct new-car scent. Every electronic component, from the infotainment system to the seat heaters, functions perfectly. Under the hood, the engine bay is detailed to a high standard, showing no signs of fluid leaks or aging. All maintenance has been performed exclusively by certified technicians, with a thick folder of records to verify its pampered history. This sale includes the original window sticker, two master keys, and all factory manuals. For the buyer seeking a flawless, investment-quality example, this is the one.",
